🏠 : @theplaygroundla

— 2022 — 

If you didn’t have your tongue out this much in a year did you even have fun? 😝 (me in 99% of this)

Okay okay but really..this last year had a lot of firsts and realizations. I spent more time with family. Chose life over work. The wins came with losses and love came with grieving. But I’m here! Continuing to grow and learn about myself. Pushing myself out of my comfort zone to be the woman I imagine myself to be. Cheers to 2023 and achieving all that makes us feel warm and fuzzy inside! 🥂

✨TAYLOR SWIFT ERAS TOUR ✨

Well shit!! hahah opening weekend happened and I can finally share that I’m on tour with @taylorswift!!!!! It feels surreal yet just right.

Taylor…I am SO happy to be working with such an incredible artists and human. You’re a queen and I’m a fan of yours in every way.

I cannot give enough props to our choreographer (and so much more) @nopenother…she is a force! A brilliant mind. An amazing leader. ALSO! Her team of @jhudmoves and @amandabalen…bless! They held us down and lifted us up all day every day. A trio of legends. 

To the 14 that I get to tear the stage up with…we’re so unique and so perfect together. It’s only the beginning 💜

#YouCanCallMeBanks
#TheOtherTaylor 🤣
#TaylorSwift #TheErasTour #TaylorNation

The other Taylor has reentered the chat 🔪👠 

🎥: @stateofgab22 (thank you 🥹)

#theerastour #erastour #taylorswift #theothertaylor #vigilante Taylor Swift The Eras Tour Vigilante Shit

6 SOLD OUT SHOW MARATHON AT SOFIIIIIIII 🤯

Let’s talk about it…

Wow I am so fucking grateful to be where I am. To close a leg of tour in my city for the first time was unreal. The joy I felt seeing friends from the different chapters of my professional journey was wild. It was like touching a piece of every job/moment that led me to this stage. Jeeze I’m not crying you’re crying!!

To each and every person that took the time to reach out, came to a show, sent me love in any capacity from show one until now…THANK YOU SO MUCH!! 🥰 I know I’ve been a bit MIA because I may or may not get a little overwhelmed outside of my kick ball change 😅 iykyk…BUT I see you and I appreciate you more than I can say. 

Thanks for coming to my #TayTalk and see you SO soon Mexico City! 🔥

#taylorswift #theerastour #tstheerastour #erastour

ERAS TOUR MOVIE WORLD PREMIERE 🎥⭐️ 10.11.23

I don’t think I’ll ever have the words to explain what it’s like when your dreams become a reality. I am endlessly grateful for these firsts, this family, this life. I’ve dreamt of being on the big screen and walking a red carpet since I was a little girl. I never knew in what capacity but it ended up being me doing exactly what I love…that’s everything I could ever ask for. This is our movie! The screams, the joy, the tears, the support we had for one another in that theater…I’ll never forget it. This is only the beginning. Taylor I love you. Eras family I love you 🫶🏽

IT’S OFFICIALLY OUT! 🥳

You’re more than the man…you’re a record breaking, box office slaying, humble, inspiring, hilarious, and kind hearted human. Oh and casually person of the year.
